_:N27d3e58544ab4bc3822357bb18f880ee <http://schema.org/description> "The Independent Football Regulator (IFR) has been established to protect and promote the sustainability of English football, for the benefit of fans and the local communities football clubs serve. IFR is an executive non-departmental public body, sponsored by the Department for Culture, Media and Sport ." .
